<沿革內容><![CDATA[1.The enacted Standards with all 8 Articles were promulgated by Order of OCAC Chiao-Si-Dang-Zi No. 09530280481 on August 24. 2006, and will put into force by the date of the execution of The Freedom of Government Information Law.]]></沿革內容>
<前言><![CDATA[]]></前言>
<法規內容>
  <條文>
    <條號>Article 1</條號>
    <條文內容><![CDATA[These Standards are enacted according to Paragraph 2 of Article 22 of the Freedom of Government Information Law(hereinafter referred to as the “Law”).]]></條文內容>
  </條文>
  <條文>
    <條號>Article 2</條號>
    <條文內容><![CDATA[The fee for viewing, copying, or photographing government information is NT$20 for two hours , time spent less than two hours is counted as two hours.]]></條文內容>
  </條文>
  <條文>
    <條號>Article 3</條號>
    <條文內容><![CDATA[The fee for duplicating or copying government information shall be charged in accordance with The Standard Table of Fees for Duplicating or Copying Government Information (see attachment).
In the preceding paragraph not specified in these Standards, fees shall be charged according to the cost of duplication or copying.]]></條文內容>
  </條文>
  <條文>
    <條號>Article 4</條號>
    <條文內容><![CDATA[If the applicant requests the duplicated or copied government information to be sent by mail, the actual mailing expenses shall be charged.]]></條文內容>
  </條文>
  <條文>
    <條號>Article 5</條號>
    <條文內容><![CDATA[The applicant that requests for the government information for academic research or public welfare purposes must attach relevant documents at the time of application. Upon approval, the applicant must pay for the mailing costs; whereas other fees shall be charged at half price.]]></條文內容>
  </條文>
  <條文>
    <條號>Article 6</條號>
    <條文內容><![CDATA[Duplication of government information for business or education promotions stipulated in Subparagraph 1 of Article 12 of the Charges and Fees Act shall be free of charge.]]></條文內容>
  </條文>
  <條文>
    <條號>Article 7</條號>
    <條文內容><![CDATA[The fees set out in these Standards shall be charged in compliance with budgetary procedures.]]></條文內容>
  </條文>
  <條文>
    <條號>Article 8</條號>
    <條文內容><![CDATA[These Standards shall be in force from the date of the enforcement of the law.]]></條文內容>
  </條文>
</法規內容>
</法規>
